# Jedinstveni LF u repou (Linux/Render) — bez LF/CRLF upozorenja na git add.
# Ne utiče na rad aplikacije; samo normalizuje krajeve linija u Git-u.

* text=auto eol=lf

*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.ico binary
*.svg binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
*.gz binary
*.mp4 binary
*.webm binary
*.pyc binary
